# Guing Design System — AI Coding Instructions for test-client

## Rules
- Always import components from `test-client-design-system`
- Do not hardcode hex color values — use CSS variables from design-tokens
- Reference `ai-manifest.json` for available components and their props
- When creating new UI, prefer composition of existing components
- Use TypeScript for all new files

## Available Tokens
- CSS Variables: use `var(--color-primary)`, `var(--font-heading-1-size)`, etc.
- TypeScript: `import { designTokens } from 'test-client-design-system'`
- JSON: raw token data in `src/design-tokens/tokens.json`

## Component Conventions
- All components should accept a `className` prop for styling overrides
- Use forwardRef for DOM element access
- Include JSDoc comments for all public props
